{"tid":1655350,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"1020遊行新策略 - 和理非遊行散去後立即18區開花","createTime":"2019-10-15T04:28:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-15T06:00:02.000Z","uid":61886,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"2ae195c1289faf4de231001623a5d758cb42abe8","tid":1655350,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T04:28:34.000Z","msg":"此方法結合和理非大遊行及遍地開花既優勢<br />\n- 和理非遊行：晒馬<br />\n- 遍地開花：前線更安全<br />\n<br />\n方法：<br />\n1. 和理非遊行聚集<br />\n2. 遊行後不留守，即時回歸所屬區域。<br />\n3. 於約定地點及時間開花。<br />\n<br />\n優點：<br />\n1. 全力和理非遊行，顯示民意。<br />\n2. 減少大遊行陣地戰，減低被捕人數。<br />\n3. 可照顧遊行的老弱婦孺。<br />\n4. 臥底於遊行時難以煽動留守。<br />\n5. 18區開花減低被捕人數。<br />\n6. 迫使警犬於多區佈防，令遊行更安全。<br />\n7. 遊行時已聚集民眾，開花必然多人。<br />\n8. 前線不用顧慮遊行時保護和理非而對峙及被捕。<br />\n<br />\n注意及共識事項：<br />\n1. 散去後交通安排。<br />\n2. 開花時間。<br />\n<br />\n歡迎討論"},{"pid":"82db62aeb0e5945ae50029ea19b1ae312f00c8a6","tid":1655350,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T04:29:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oWDDhxL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoWDDhxL.jpg&h=5983aa27&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d64132437dd3894470385eecf43e3282f37b688c","tid":1655350,"uid":45078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T04:29:52.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"af7c77b03ae57f7b10c7f5b1d3370f4d4e9e2a81","tid":1655350,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T04:29:58.000Z","msg":"如果可以達成共識<br />\n咁我地行動會更加細密"},{"pid":"91ba69fbf5aa5a46b5f1e8f7062387b807ea07b4","tid":1655350,"uid":146917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T04:30:09.000Z","msg":"首先和理非要出黎"},{"pid":"f186b2325e622fc1fdcad8883cf85ca2ca29eb60","tid":1655350,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"91ba69fbf5aa5a46b5f1e8f7062387b807ea07b4","tid":1655350,"uid":146917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T04:30:09.000Z","msg":"首先和理非要出黎"},"citedBy":0,"r